column3: past_due_days (cutoff on 12/8/2016, negative means paid early)
column4: education (0 = high school or below, 1 = some college, 2 = bachelor, 3 = master or above)
column7: money_in_checking_account (0 = less than 0 or no account, 1 = between 0 and 10000, 2 = more than 10000)
column8: credit_history (0 = no credits taken or all credits paid back on time, 1 = existing credits paid back on time until now, 2 = delay in paying back in the past, 3 = critical account/credits at other banks)
column10: money_in_savings (0 = unknown or no savings account, 1 = less than 1000, 2 = between 1000 and 5000, 3 = between 5000 and 10000, 4 = over 10000)
column11: years_at_present_employment (0 = unemployed, 1 = less than 1 year, 2 = between 1 and 4 years, 3 = between 4 and 7 years, 4 = more than 7 years)
